The band is currently promoting their latest album, ''[[Snakes & Arrows]]''. An intercontinental concert [[Snakes And Arrows Tour|tour]] began [[June 13]], [[2007]] in [[Atlanta, Georgia]].<ref>Official Rush Website [http://www.rush.com] Accessed [[26 March]] [[2007]]</ref>  

