* [[Alex Lifeson]] <U+2013> six- and twelve-string acoustic and electric guitars, [[mandolin]], [[mandola]], [[Bouzouki]], backing vocals, bass and synthesizer pedals (summer 1968-present)
* [[Neil Peart]] <U+2013> drums, electronic and acoustic percussion (July 1974<U+2013>present)

